<div id="posts">
  <main style="margin-bottom: 4rem;">
    <div class="section_title container">
      <h1 class="aboutme">About me</h1>
      <p class="p_aboutme">
        My name is Diego Salinas and I'm a Jr. Web developer. I'm from Mexico and I'm currently looking for a job. You can find me on [
        <a href="https://twitter.com/mantequillah_" target="_blank"><i class="fa-brands fa-twitter"></i></a>,
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/diego-salinas09/" target="_blank"><i class="fa-brands fa-linkedin-in"></i></a>,
        <a href="https://github.com/diegoOG09" target="_blank"><i class="fa-brands fa-github-alt"></i></a> ].
      </p>
      <p class="p_aboutme">
        On this page you can find some information about me and a few blog posts I wrote. Most of them are about topics that I'm most interested in, such as web development, Ruby on Rails or Javascript.
      </p>
      <div class="grid_things container">
        <div class="things">
          <h2><i class="fas fa-keyboard"></i>I handle...</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>Ruby on Rails</li>
            <li>Javascript</li>
            <li>HTML/CSS</li>
            <li>GNU/Linux</li>
            <li>Terminal</li>
            <li>Vue soon</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="things">
          <h2><i class="fas fa-fire"></i>Passionate about...</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>Coding</li>
            <li>Cinema</li>
            <li>Videogames</li>
            <li>Books</li>
            <li>Music</li>
        </div>
        <div class="things">
          <h2><i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i>Thinking about...</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>Vue</li>
            <li>Unit test</li>
            <li>Full-stack</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container section_title">
      <h1 class="aboutme">Blog posts</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="articles-grid container">
      <% @posts.each do |post| %>
        <div class="article-card">
          <div class="date">
            <%= post.created_at.strftime("%d - %B - %Y") %>
          </div>
          <div class="article-info">
            <h2><%= post.title %></h2>
            <h3><%= post.description %></h3>
            <p> <%= link_to "Read more...", article_path(article_id: post.id) %> </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      <% end %>
      <%= will_paginate @posts %>
    </div>
  </main>

</div>
